query: SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS movie_company, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(t.title) AS complete_euro_dark_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, company_name AS cn, company_type AS ct, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND t.production_year < 2005 AND (t.title like '%night%' OR t.title like '%darkness%') AND (cn.name like '%Walt Disney Studios%' OR cn.name like '%A24%' OR cn.name like '%Paramount Pictures%') AND it1.info in ('LD subtitles','LD official retail price','salary history','votes') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','complete+verified') AND it2.info not in ('languages','LD original title','pictorial','LD official retail price','LD sound encoding','LD frequency response','soundtrack','birth notes','mpaa','biographical movies','adaption','LD sharpness') AND kt.kind in ('movie','tv movie','tv series','video game','video movie','tv mini series') AND ct.kind not in ('distributors','special effects companies','miscellaneous companies') AND mi.info in ('Tatar','Flemish','Hungarian') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','complete+verified','crew') AND mi_idx.info < '4.0' AND mc.note not like '%Japan%' AND mc.note not like '%Canada%' AND mc.note not like '%Italy%' AND (k.keyword like '%vengeful%' OR k.keyword like '%future%' OR k.keyword like '%prison%')
